    • Method Detail

      • isOntClassExisting

        static boolean isOntClassExisting(String className,
                                  org.apache.jena.ontology.OntModel ontModel)
                           throws IOException,
                                  org.openbase.jul.exception.NotAvailableException
        Method verifies, if the input className is a valid class element of the ontology. Namespace prefix is automatically added, if missing. Consider case sensitive of the class name! The ontology can be set as parameter or if null the actual ontology is downloaded.
        Parameters:
        className - The class name, which should be verified as OntClass (existing in ontology).
        ontModel - The ontology, which contains all elements. If null, the actual ontology is downloaded.
        Returns:
        true if parameter is a valid ontClass name of the ontology. Otherwise false.
        Throws:
        IOException - Exception is thrown, if their is no connection to the server.
        org.openbase.jul.exception.NotAvailableException - Exception is thrown, if the className is null.

      • isOntPropertyExisting

        static boolean isOntPropertyExisting(String propertyName,
                                     org.apache.jena.ontology.OntModel ontModel)
                              throws org.openbase.jul.exception.NotAvailableException,
                                     IOException
        Method verifies, if the parameter is a valid property element of the ontology. Namespace prefix is automatically added, if missing. Consider case sensitive of the property name! The ontology can be set as parameter or if null the actual ontology is downloaded.
        Parameters:
        propertyName - The property name, which should be verified as OntProperty (existing in ontology).
        ontModel - The ontology, which contains all elements. If null, the actual ontology is downloaded.
        Returns:
        true if parameter is a valid ontProperty name of the ontology. Otherwise false.
        Throws:
        IOException - Exception is thrown, if their is no connection to the server.
        org.openbase.jul.exception.NotAvailableException - Exception is thrown, if the propertyName is null.
